代码如下

```cpp
int phi(int x)
{
    int re=x;
    for(int i=2;i*i<=x;i++)
    {
        if(x%i==0)
        {
            re=re/i*(i-1);
            while(x%i==0)x/=i;
        }
    }
    if(x>1)re=re/x*(x-1);
    return re;
}
```
